{"tid":1674942,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"提早收工","createTime":"2019-10-25T13:56:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T16:02:38.000Z","uid":254738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9245c31a02c93bc3fe874c66f189ded8ecc71740","tid":1674942,"uid":254738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:56:16.000Z","msg":"話說我同個女仔同事曖昧左一段時間<br />\n之前會襯佢收工前搵佢傾下<br />\n貪個時公司少人d，少d閒言閒語<br />\n<br />\n曖昧左一段時間，宜家行開行埋<br />\n佢都避開我<br />\n可以話應該無行<br />\n平時佢好夜收工，之後早左收<br />\n我有早一d搵過佢傾，然後佢又再早d收工<br />\n應該都係想避開我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我呢份人鍾意得佢，就希望佢好<br />\n唔想煩到佢，我選擇唔再追<br />\n於是我提早早過佢收工，d野返屋企做<br />\n等佢見唔到我唔洗怕我搵佢<br />\n之後佢就可以如常自由收工<br />\n<br />\n但係佢發現左我早收工<br />\n佢之後又再早d收<br />\n搞到好早就走左人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實佢咩心態呢？<br />\n我應該點做呢？<br />\n<br />\n(我已經放棄追求，所以最緊要係佢好我好大家好，做唔成情侶，我都想做返普通朋友/同事)"},{"pid":"0d9df871cc4033cdba93eb816acc64d4598efe8f","tid":1674942,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:03:31.000Z","msg":"你應該繼續幫佢再早d收工"},{"pid":"691bd48792dd0e17fc9e17d507bc4a28a6dc47c0","tid":1674942,"uid":254738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:23:02.000Z","msg":"有無可能係佢覺得我提早收工就係我讓佢<br />\n而佢又唔想欠左我，於是就早過我呢？<br />\n但係咁樣又膠膠地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n宜家行過我旁邊都急步<br />\n有時仲尊登繞路避我<br />\n明顯feel到佢唔想同我有瓜葛<br />\n其實我見到都真係幾灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢日日都係，我盲既都知啦<br />\n我都真係想佢顧下我感受.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e615ae85754d771aa61526890e529aec73a6a197","tid":1674942,"uid":254738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d9df871cc4033cdba93eb816acc64d4598efe8f","tid":1674942,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:03:31.000Z","msg":"你應該繼續幫佢再早d收工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:24:00.000Z","msg":"點解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f6a6b8e6d519acbd290d95b369736bec4af29f","tid":1674942,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e615ae85754d771aa61526890e529aec73a6a197","tid":1674942,"uid":254738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d9df871cc4033cdba93eb816acc64d4598efe8f","tid":1674942,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:03:31.000Z","msg":"你應該繼續幫佢再早d收工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:24:00.000Z","msg":"點解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:31:32.000Z","msg":"6點變5點<br />\n5點變4點<br />\n<br />\n幾爽呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7798b35884b6f2172d3b10f0937a31849b88b4","tid":1674942,"uid":254738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:16:52.000Z","msg":"早收工都要做架，係返左屋企做<br />\n公司做野效率高d<br />\n<br />\n公司做野，水電都慳埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00504f107ca451a158ff7896fce4c6bd4a464186","tid":1674942,"uid":254738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T16:02:38.000Z","msg":"各位巴打俾d意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\